st one of the vaccines causes a different amount of antibodies to be produc=
ed (at least one group originates from a different distribution and has a d=
ifferent median)</p><h3>Step 2:</h3><p>Here we organize our data into ascen=
ding order then give each a rank.</p><div class=3D"rds-article--output" ari=
a-label=3D"output"><pre><code class=3D"language-plaintext">
